{"tid":312363,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"好憎聽到啲人講「上天係好公平」","createTime":"2017-07-07T11:29:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-07T11:40:40.000Z","uid":61394,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f030ef9410e98e7d3372d67251619fd3c5714ee4","tid":312363,"uid":61394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T11:29:55.000Z","msg":"每當我提出一個缺點嘅時候，例如條女個波好撚平<br />\n<br />\n總有啲仆街會跳出嚟話「上天好公平，佢高同瘦所以平波」。我真係笑到鳩都飛埋出嚟，咁又肥冇波又冇樣果啲肥絲點撚樣計呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n根撚本我每提一個缺點，佢地就會講返一個優點出嚟，然後仲要一副看透世事嘅西樣，你咁撚有看法不如產光個頭出家襌修啦 屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果上天真係咁撚公平，我就唔應該出世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"436d18a319b995a916eb974f3390b7084cca89ad","tid":312363,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T11:31:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"29f09355c96033fca914266a9426535394748ba5","tid":312363,"uid":123308,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T11:32:17.000Z","msg":"加埋「人人都係一日廿四小時」"},{"pid":"8bb199de102b2b9f582f0c85739bc18665a95afa","tid":312363,"uid":5523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T11:32:32.000Z","msg":"公平咩？"},{"pid":"64d4e56e4843e7a46a5fd90359dcb1dfb30266f4","tid":312363,"uid":47160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T11:34:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>加埋「人人都係一日廿四小時」</blockquote><br />\n點解人地得你唔得？"},{"pid":"f597983cd09a05cdc838ea5fcca5869c06e74169","tid":312363,"uid":61394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T11:38:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>加埋「人人都係一日廿四小時」</blockquote><br />\n點解人地得你唔得？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢句同琴晚見到你條女上咗酒店係同一level <br />\n下一秒點都要開波打柒佢"},{"pid":"ea67396211290fd6f565e7877c9fd7fe0ba00ada","tid":312363,"uid":50663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T11:40:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>加埋「人人都係一日廿四小時」</blockquote><br />\n點解人地得你唔得？</blockquote><br />\n有苦先有樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}